snippet.title: Neon Boost - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Neon Boost is a frenetic First Person Platformer based on mechanics like Rocket-Jump or Wall-Run. Run across 3 different worlds to get the best times on the world!

Available May 20th on Steam for free:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1057850/Neon_Boost/

Developed by: @JRamonEspinosa @Montyrell @bernieltartas
Music by:  https://soundcloud.com/alexei_ost (Twitter: @alexei_ost)
